dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Cajon quadrangle, San Bernardino County, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle CAJON, CA 1988, DMA 2552 IV SW-Series V895" "Prepared in cooperation with the Angeles National Forest." "John Foster honorary map." "First printing, October 2003." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, index to sources of geology, and 1 col. cross section. Includes "pertinent references."
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
